data.description: Welcome to your amazing new single story home with Superstition Mountain views right out your front door. This is the property of your dreams...loads of updates & space in the open floor plan with lots of large windows, 10ft ceilings & tons of natural light to take in the beauty that surrounds you.  With 3 ideally laid out bedrooms, it offers the perfect amount of space for a family or great winter getaway oasis.  A charming kitchen with updated appliances, a breakfast/sitting nook, & raised bar area opens to the bright modern living room complete with fireplace. Head out the 9ft patio doors to an entertainer's dream with the amazing updated backyard oasis complete with covered patio, pergola, putting green & pavers to enjoy all that outdoor Arizona living has to offer. Located in the Superstition Foothills this home is in the ideal community with low HOA fees, heated community pool & spa, loads of fantastic hiking and walking trails & just right around the corner from shopping, dining & hiking trails. Come see for yourself all this home & ideal community has to offer!
